import React from 'react'; const DatabaseSchema = () => { return (

Database Schema

Parameter Description
timestamp The timestamp of the kline/candlestick.
open Opening price during the kline interval.
high Highest price during the kline interval.
low Lowest price during the kline interval.
close Closing price during the kline interval.
volume Trading volume during the kline interval.
close_time Closing time of the kline/candlestick.
quote_asset_volume Volume of the quote asset traded.
number_of_trades Number of trades during the kline interval.
taker_buy_base_asset_volume Volume of the base asset bought with taker buy orders.
taker_buy_quote_asset_volume Volume of the quote asset bought with taker buy orders.
); }; export default DatabaseSchema;
